            <abstract>
                <p>Miracles worked by ʾAbuna Madḫānina ʾƎgziʾ after an order by King <persName ref="PRS4015Fasilada">Fāsiladas</persName> 
                    to plant beautiful trees around the
                    <placeName ref="INS0344AksumS">cathedral of ʾAksum</placeName> during its reconstruction. The trees were taken from the
                    surroundings of the <placeName ref="LOC2242DabraB">convent of Bankʷal</placeName>. The governor of Tǝgrāy 
                    is named as
                    <persName ref="PRS14821LabaseK">Labāse Krǝstos</persName>, the <foreign xml:lang="gez">nǝbura ʾǝd</foreign> of ʾAksum as
                    <persName ref="PRS14822EssetaM">ʿƎśśeta Māryām</persName> and the <foreign xml:lang="gez">sǝyyum</foreign> of
                    Šǝre as <persName ref="PRS14823LessanaK">Lǝssāna Krǝstos of Ṣallamt</persName>.</p>
